xyz.swatt.selenium

Class WebDriverTransitionalWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.selenium.WebDriverWrapper
      • xyz.swatt.selenium.WebDriverTransitionalWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable

    public class WebDriverTransitionalWrapper
extends WebDriverWrapper
    This Class extends WebDriverWrapper and contains all of it's functionality.

    The only difference is that this class has the getWebDriver() method.

    The purpose of this class is to be used temporarily, while transitioning an existing project to SWATT.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)
